[normal]Editorial highlights[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]This year saw 
[normal]all editorial elements of 
[normal]Global News 
[normal]- World Service, World News and bbc.com/news 
[normal]- 
[normal]become more 
[normal]united than ever before when they came 
[normal]together
[normal] under one roof in New Broadcasting House. This launched the concept of ‘The World’s Newsroom’, enabling editorial collaboration across the news group, both within Global News and between Global News and UK News.  
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]WS Languages, BBC Monitoring and
[normal] Newsgathering worked closely together to ensure that audiences were able to access the latest information and analysis. 
[normal]Some of the highlights included:
